#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.partitionmanager.appdata.xml:11
msgid "KDE Partition Manager"
msgstr "KDE Partition Manager (gerente de partition de KDE)"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.partitionmanager.appdata.xml:12
msgid "Manage disks, partitions, and file systems"
msgstr "Gere discos, partitiones e systemas de file"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.partitionmanager.appdata.xml:14
msgid ""
"KDE Partition Manager is a utility to help you manage the disks, partitions, "
"and file systems on your computer. It allows you to easily create, copy, "
"move, delete, back up, restore, and resize them without losing data. It "
"supports a large number of file systems, including ext2/3/4, btrfs, "
"reiserfs, NTFS, FAT16/32, JFS, XFS and more."
msgstr ""
"KDE Partition Manager es un utilitate per adjutar te a gerer le discos, "
"pertitiones e systema de files sur tu computator. Illo te permitte in modo "
"facile crear, copiar, mover, deler, afcer copia de reserva,restabilir e "
"redimensionar lor sin perder datos. Illo suppoirta un grande numero de "
"systema de files, includente ext2/3/4, btrfs, reiserfs, NTFS, FAT16/32, JFS, "
"XFS e alteres."

